text: L-functions and modular forms database is an extensive database of mathematical objects arising in number theory. It can be used for searching modular forms, elliptic curves, number fields (and fields), L-functions... == LuCaNT 2023 == The first conference on the LMFDB, Computation, and Number Theory (LuCaNT) is currently being planned for July 10 to July 14, 2023 at ICERM in Providence, Rhode Island, United States.
